<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"/>
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#7a1a1a">
<title>Sabraoui &amp; Co. · WM 2026 Tippspiel</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Amiri:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }

  :root {
    --maroc-red: #c1272d;
    --maroc-red-deep: #7a1a1a;
    --maroc-red-dark: #3d0c0c;
    --maroc-green: #006233;
    --maroc-green-glow: #00a050;
    --sand: #f4e4c1;
    --gold: #e6b54a;
    --gold-glow: #f5c95f;
    --brazil-yellow: #ffdf00;
    --brazil-green: #009c3b;
    --danger: #ff4757;
    --success: #2ed573;
    --text: #f4e4c1;
    --text-muted: #c9a87a;
    --card-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    --card-border: rgba(244,228,193,0.15);
  }

  html, body { overscroll-behavior: none; }

  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top, #8a1f1f 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, #2a0808 0%, transparent 55%),
      var(--maroc-red-dark);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 18px 12px 60px;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    body { padding: 14px 8px 60px; }
  }

  body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(230,181,74,0.06) 2px, transparent 3px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, rgba(0,98,51,0.05) 2px, transparent 3px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(244,228,193,0.04) 1px, transparent 2px);
    background-size: 80px 80px, 80px 80px, 40px 40px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  body::after {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    top: -120px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><polygon points='50,5 61,38 95,38 67,58 78,90 50,70 22,90 33,58 5,38 39,38' fill='none' stroke='%23006233' stroke-width='1.5' opacity='0.15'/></svg>");
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    transform: rotate(15deg);
  }

  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* ─── HEADER: SABRAOUI prominent ────────────────────────── */
  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .family-crest {
    font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .family-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 5.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sand) 0%, var(--gold) 35%, var(--maroc-red) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(230,181,74,0.15);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    position: relative;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .family-decoration {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
  }

  .family-motto {
    font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
    color: var(--gold-glow);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 4.5vw, 1.6rem);
    margin: 8px auto 4px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 0 8px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(230,181,74,0.25);
  }

  .family-motto-translate {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .family-decoration .line {
    height: 1px;
    width: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
  }

  .family-decoration .star {
    color: var(--maroc-green);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .family-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .family-subtitle .flag {
    font-size: 1rem;
    vertical-align: -1px;
    margin: 0 4px;
  }

  /* ─── User-Bar (oben rechts) ─────────────────────────────── */
  .user-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .user-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .user-avatar-mini {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--maroc-red), var(--gold));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--sand);
  }

  .user-name { color: var(--sand); font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: 0.9rem; max-width: 140px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
  .user-badge {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #2a1500;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .user-name { max-width: 90px; font-size: 0.82rem; }
    .sync-bar span:last-child { display: none; }
  }

  .sync-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .sync-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .sync-dot.online { background: var(--success); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--success); }
  .sync-dot.syncing { background: var(--gold); animation: pulse 1s infinite; }
  .sync-dot.error { background: var(--danger); }

  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } }

  .link-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px 6px;
  }
  .link-btn:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .link-btn.admin-link {
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .link-btn.admin-link.is-admin {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #c89530);
    color: #2a1500;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(230,181,74,0.4);
  }

  /* ─── Tabs ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    padding: 6px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .tab {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: max-content;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .tab.active {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--maroc-red), var(--maroc-red-deep));
    color: var(--sand);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(193,39,45,0.4);
  }

  .tab-content { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .section-title::before {
    content: "";
    width: 6px;
    height: 22px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--maroc-red), var(--gold));
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .section-hint {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ─── Match-Karten ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .match-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .match-card.is-morocco {
    border-color: rgba(193,39,45,0.5);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(193,39,45,0.12), rgba(0,98,51,0.06));
  }

  .match-card.live {
    border-color: var(--maroc-red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(193,39,45,0.3);
  }

  .match-card.finished {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .match-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .match-stage {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .match-status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
  }

  .status-upcoming { background: rgba(244,228,193,0.1); color: var(--sand); }
  .status-live { background: var(--maroc-red); color: white; }
  .status-finished { background: rgba(0,98,51,0.2); color: var(--maroc-green-glow); }

  .live-blip {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 1s infinite;
  }

  .match-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .team-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .team-block.away {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .team-flag-emoji {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* ─── Country Badge mit Flagge + Kürzel ─────────────────── */
  .country-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    min-width: 52px;
    height: 32px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244,228,193,0.10), rgba(244,228,193,0.03));
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--sand);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .country-badge .cb-flag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 22px;
    height: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    line-height: 0;
  }

  .country-badge .cb-flag svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .country-badge .cb-code {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  .country-badge.is-morocco {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--maroc-red), var(--maroc-red-deep));
    border-color: var(--maroc-red);
    color: var(--sand);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(193,39,45,0.3);
  }

  .country-badge.placeholder {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    border-style: dashed;
    min-width: 48px;
    padding: 0 6px;
  }

  .country-badge.sm {
    min-width: 42px;
    height: 24px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0 7px;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .country-badge.sm .cb-flag {
    width: 18px;
    height: 12px;
  }

  .team-block .team-info {
    text-align: left;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .team-block.away .team-info {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .team-block .team-info-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .team-block .team-info-name { font-size: 0.88rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
    .team-flag-emoji { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .match-score { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .match-score-area { min-width: 60px; }
  }

  .team-block.is-morocco .team-info-name {
    color: #ff8a8f;
  }

  .match-score-area {
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 80px;
  }

  .match-score {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--sand);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .match-score .sep { color: var(--gold); margin: 0 4px; }
  .match-score.placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .match-meta-bottom {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .match-tipp-area {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }

  .match-tipp-input {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 400px) {
    .match-tipp-input {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      row-gap: 8px;
    }
    .match-tipp-input button {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }

  .mini-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px; /* mind. 16px verhindert iOS-Auto-Zoom */
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .mini-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); }

  .my-tipp-display {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .my-tipp-display .label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .my-tipp-display .value {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--sand);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .points-badge {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #2a1500;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  .points-badge.zero { background: rgba(244,228,193,0.15); color: var(--text-muted); }

  .lock-msg {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 10px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ─── Buttons ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .btn {
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 11px 16px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .btn.primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--maroc-red), var(--maroc-red-deep));
    color: var(--sand);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(193,39,45,0.35);
  }
  .btn.primary:active { transform: scale(0.97); }

  .btn.gold {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #c89530);
    color: #2a1500;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(230,181,74,0.4);
  }
  .btn.gold:active { transform: scale(0.97); }

  .btn.ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }
  .btn.ghost:active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

  .btn.full { width: 100%; }
  .btn.sm { padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 0.75rem; }

  /* ─── ALLE TIPPS · Matrix ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .alltipps-legend {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .legend-item {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .legend-dot.exact { background: var(--success); }
  .legend-dot.diff { background: var(--gold); }
  .legend-dot.tendency { background: #6a8caf; }
  .legend-dot.wrong { background: rgba(255,71,87,0.5); }
  .legend-dot.pending { background: rgba(244,228,193,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--text-muted); }

  .alltipps-wrap {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 8px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .alltipps-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 4px;
    min-width: 100%;
  }

  .alltipps-table th {
    background: rgba(193,39,45,0.15);
    color: var(--sand);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 8px 6px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    vertical-align: top;
    min-width: 78px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .alltipps-table th.player-col {
    background: rgba(0,98,51,0.18);
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 10px;
    position: sticky;
    left: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    min-width: 100px;
    max-width: 140px;
  }

  .alltipps-table th.player-col-empty {
    background: transparent;
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-flags {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-badges {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-vs {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-date {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-result {
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 4px;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(230,181,74,0.3);
  }

  .alltipps-table th .th-result.pending {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    border-top-color: rgba(244,228,193,0.15);
  }

  .alltipps-table td {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    padding: 8px 6px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    position: relative;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .alltipps-table td.player-cell {
    background: rgba(0,98,51,0.12);
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 10px;
    position: sticky;
    left: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    color: var(--sand);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .alltipps-table td.player-cell.me {
    background: rgba(230,181,74,0.18);
    color: var(--gold-glow);
  }

  .alltipps-table td.player-cell .player-points {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .alltipps-table tr.me-row td:not(.player-cell) {
    background: rgba(230,181,74,0.08);
  }

  /* Zell-Farben nach Punkten */
  .alltipps-table td.tipp-3 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(46,213,115,0.35), rgba(46,213,115,0.15));
    color: var(--success);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46,213,115,0.5);
  }

  .alltipps-table td.tipp-2 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(230,181,74,0.3), rgba(230,181,74,0.1));
    color: var(--gold-glow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,181,74,0.4);
  }

  .alltipps-table td.tipp-1 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(106,140,175,0.25), rgba(106,140,175,0.08));
    color: #a8c0db;
    border: 1px solid rgba(106,140,175,0.3);
  }

  .alltipps-table td.tipp-0 {
    background: rgba(255,71,87,0.1);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.2);
  }

  .alltipps-table td.tipp-none {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .alltipps-table td.tipp-locked {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .alltipps-table td .tipp-pts {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-top: 1px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .alltipps-table td .admin-edit {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2px;
    right: 2px;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    line-height: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: none;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }

  .alltipps-table td:hover .admin-edit.is-admin {
    display: block;
  }

  /* Touch-Geräte: Admin-Edit immer sichtbar wenn Admin */
  @media (hover: none) {
    .alltipps-table td .admin-edit.is-admin {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile-Anpassungen für Matrix-Tabelle */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .alltipps-table th { min-width: 64px; padding: 6px 3px; font-size: 0.68rem; }
    .alltipps-table th.player-col { min-width: 80px; max-width: 100px; }
    .alltipps-table td { padding: 6px 3px; font-size: 0.85rem; min-width: 64px; }
    .alltipps-table td.player-cell { font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .alltipps-table th .th-result { font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .alltipps-legend { font-size: 0.65rem; gap: 6px 10px; }
  }

  /* ─── Leaderboard ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .leaderboard {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .lb-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 30px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }
  .lb-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .lb-row.me {
    background: rgba(230,181,74,0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding-left: 12px;
    border-color: rgba(230,181,74,0.2);
  }

  .lb-rank {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lb-row.gold .lb-rank { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .lb-row.silver .lb-rank { color: #c0c0c0; }
  .lb-row.bronze .lb-rank { color: #cd7f32; }

  .lb-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--sand);
  }

  .lb-points {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ─── BRACKET ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .bracket-wrap {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 12px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .bracket-hint {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .bracket {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 200px);
    gap: 18px;
    min-width: 1060px;
    padding: 10px 0;
  }

  .round-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-around;
  }

  .round-col-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230,181,74,0.2);
  }

  .br-match {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    margin: 6px 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .br-match:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .br-match.has-morocco {
    border-color: rgba(193,39,45,0.6);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(193,39,45,0.18), rgba(0,98,51,0.05));
  }

  .br-match.morocco-advanced {
    border-color: var(--maroc-red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(193,39,45,0.3);
  }

  .br-team {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3px 0;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .br-team.winner { color: var(--gold); }
  .br-team.loser { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: line-through; }
  .br-team.morocco { color: #ff8a8f; }

  .br-team-name {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  .br-team-score {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    min-width: 18px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .br-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--card-border);
    margin: 3px 0;
  }

  .br-info {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .br-final-trophy {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ─── Modals ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    z-index: 100;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .modal-overlay.show { display: flex; }

  .modal {
    background: var(--maroc-red-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 22px 20px;
    max-width: 420px;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }

  .modal-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--sand);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .modal-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .input {
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 11px 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px; /* mind. 16px verhindert iOS-Auto-Zoom */
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); }
  .input::placeholder { color: rgba(201,168,122,0.5); }

  .field-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ─── Spielplan ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .schedule-group {
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .schedule-group-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230,181,74,0.2);
  }

  /* ─── Empty State ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .empty {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 16px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    border: 1px dashed var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* ─── Toast ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.92);
    color: var(--sand);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .toast.show { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
  .toast.error { border-color: var(--danger); }

  /* ─── Onboarding-Banner ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .setup-banner {
    background: rgba(255,71,87,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.4);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .setup-banner.green {
    background: rgba(0,98,51,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(0,160,80,0.4);
  }

  .setup-banner code {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ─── Admin-Panel ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .admin-panel {
    background: rgba(230,181,74,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,181,74,0.3);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .admin-panel-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  /* ─── Stat-Karten ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .stats-grid { gap: 5px; }
    .stat { padding: 10px 4px; }
    .stat-num { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ─── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 30px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  footer .arabic {
    font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ─── HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <header>
    <div class="family-crest">عائلة</div>
    <div class="family-name">Sabraoui &amp; Co.</div>
    <div class="family-motto" dir="rtl" lang="ar">اللّي زرب فالتّيب كيضيّع النقط</div>
    <div class="family-motto-translate">„Wer voreilig tippt, verliert Punkte."</div>
    <div class="family-decoration">
      <span class="line"></span>
      <span class="star">★</span>
      <span class="line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="family-subtitle">
      <span class="flag">🇲🇦</span>WM 2026 · TIPPSPIEL<span class="flag">🇲🇦</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ─── User-Bar ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="user-bar">
    <div class="user-info">
      <div class="user-avatar-mini" id="user-avatar">?</div>
      <div>
        <div class="user-name" id="user-name-display">Nicht angemeldet</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;">
      <div class="sync-bar"><span class="sync-dot" id="sync-dot"></span><span id="sync-text">OFFLINE</span></div>
      <button class="link-btn admin-link" id="btn-admin-login-top" title="Admin-Modus">🔐</button>
      <button class="link-btn" id="btn-user-settings" title="Name ändern">⚙</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Setup-Banner (nur wenn nicht konfiguriert) ───────── -->
  <div class="setup-banner" id="setup-banner" style="display:none;">
    <strong>⚠️ Einmalige Einrichtung nötig:</strong> Trage oben im HTML-Code unter <code>CONFIG.binId</code> und <code>CONFIG.apiKey</code> deine JSONBin-Daten ein, sonst werden Daten nur lokal gespeichert.
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Tabs ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="tabs" id="tabs">
    <button class="tab active" data-tab="spielplan">📅 Spielplan</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="alletipps">👥 Alle Tipps</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="leaderboard">🏆 Tabelle</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="bracket">🌳 Bracket</button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="info">ℹ Info</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── TAB: Spielplan ────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="tab-content active" data-content="spielplan">
    <div class="section-title">Marokkos Weg + alle K.O.-Spiele</div>
    <div class="section-hint">Tippe Marokkos Gruppenphase sowie alle K.O.-Spiele, sobald die Paarungen feststehen. 3P exaktes Ergebnis · 2P richtige Tordifferenz · 1P richtige Tendenz. Tipps für K.O.-Spiele sperren <strong>30 Min vor Anpfiff</strong>.</div>

    <div id="schedule-content"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── TAB: Alle Tipps (Matrix-Übersicht) ─────────────────── -->
  <div class="tab-content" data-content="alletipps">
    <div class="section-title">Alle Tipps der Familie</div>
    <div class="section-hint">Hier siehst du auf einen Blick, wer was getippt hat. Tipps anderer kannst du ansehen, aber nur deine eigenen ändern (im Spielplan-Tab). Tabelle scrollt seitwärts, wenn viele Spiele eingetragen sind.</div>

    <div class="alltipps-legend">
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot exact"></span>Exakt (3P)</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot diff"></span>Tordifferenz (2P)</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot tendency"></span>Tendenz (1P)</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot wrong"></span>Falsch (0P)</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot pending"></span>Offen</span>
    </div>

    <div class="alltipps-wrap">
      <div id="alltipps-content"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── TAB: Leaderboard ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="tab-content" data-content="leaderboard">
    <div class="section-title">Familien-Tabelle</div>

    <div class="stats-grid" id="stats-grid"></div>

    <div class="leaderboard" id="leaderboard-list"></div>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Tipps des Familien-Champions</div>
    <div class="section-hint">Wer aktuell führt und welche Tipps abgegeben wurden.</div>
    <div id="champion-tipps"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── TAB: Bracket ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="tab-content" data-content="bracket">
    <div class="section-title">K.O.-Phase Bracket</div>
    <div class="section-hint">Komplettes Turnier-Baumdiagramm aller 16 Achtelfinale-Paarungen. Marokko-Spiele sind rot hervorgehoben. <strong>Admin:</strong> Klick auf jedes Spiel → Anpfiff-Zeit eintragen (= Tipp-Lock 30 Min davor) und/oder Endergebnis setzen.</div>

    <div id="admin-bracket-controls"></div>

    <div class="bracket-wrap">
      <div class="bracket-hint">← seitwärts wischen für volles Bracket →</div>
      <div class="bracket" id="bracket"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── TAB: Info ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="tab-content" data-content="info">
    <div class="section-title">Spielregeln Tippspiel</div>
    <div class="match-card">
      <div style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; letter-spacing:0.15em; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:10px; font-size:1.1rem;">Punktevergabe</div>
      <div style="display:grid; gap:8px; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;">
        <div><span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; color:var(--gold); font-size:1.1rem;">3 PUNKTE</span> · Exaktes Ergebnis getippt (z.B. 2:1 → 2:1)</div>
        <div><span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; color:var(--gold); font-size:1.1rem;">2 PUNKTE</span> · Richtige Tordifferenz (z.B. 3:2 statt 2:1)</div>
        <div><span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; color:var(--gold); font-size:1.1rem;">1 PUNKT</span> · Richtige Tendenz (Sieger oder Unentschieden korrekt)</div>
        <div><span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem;">0 PUNKTE</span> · Komplett daneben getippt</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Familienmitglieder einladen</div>
    <div class="match-card">
      <div style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:12px;">Teile diesen Link mit der Familie. Jeder gibt seinen Namen ein und kann sofort mittippen:</div>
      <button class="btn gold full" id="btn-share-link">📤 Link Teilen</button>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Admin-Bereich</div>
    <div class="match-card" id="admin-info-card">
      <div style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;">
        Als Admin (nur Mehdi Sabraoui) kannst du:
        <ul style="margin:10px 0 0 20px; color:var(--text-muted);">
          <li>Endergebnisse aller Spiele eintragen</li>
          <li>K.O.-Runde befüllen (wer kommt weiter)</li>
          <li>Tipps anderer User korrigieren oder löschen</li>
          <li>Tippspiel zurücksetzen</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn ghost sm" id="btn-admin-login" style="margin-top:14px;">🔐 Admin-Modus Aktivieren</button>
        <button class="btn ghost sm" id="btn-admin-logout" style="margin-top:14px; display:none;">Admin-Modus Verlassen</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Über</div>
    <div class="match-card" style="font-size:0.85rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--text-muted);">
      <span class="family-crest" style="display:block; margin-bottom:6px;">عائلة الصبراوي</span>
      Tippspiel der Familie Sabraoui zur Fußball-WM 2026 in Kanada, Mexiko und den USA.<br>
      Daten werden via JSONBin synchronisiert.<br>
      <span style="color:var(--gold); display:block; margin-top:10px;">يلا المغرب! 🦁</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <span class="arabic">بالتوفيق المنتخب المغربي</span>
    SABRAOUI &amp; CO. · WM 2026 · Made with ❤️
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- ─── Modals ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->

<!-- User-Setup Modal -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-user">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-title">🇲🇦 Willkommen!</div>
